text:
- Before I came to AWS,
I was a college student.
This is my first job right outta college.

- I came in through the
internship programs.
You have an opportunity to develop

as an early career individual
and to accelerate your career.

- [Khayla] I have an opportunity
to constantly be surrounded

by the smartest people
I've ever met in my life
and learn from them and grow from them.

- Different type of people
bring different things
to the table.
- Coming to a big company like this,
I thought I would just be another number.

These communities, these
affinity groups are here
to provide a special place for people,

it's just another way that I'm
able to feel accepted here.
- I get to work on the coolest technology,
I get to work with the coolest people
and I get to work for the coolest company,
so yes, I love it.

- You throw something at me
and now I have the confidence

that I will get the job done
and I will get it done well.
I'm limitless, that's what I learned.
- I truly believe that with the skills
and the learning you get here,

you could truly go anywhere,
you're unstoppable.
